# Discover and connect workspaces

The topics in this section are about how to discover and connect your
cloud platforms to so the scanning process can be performed.

::: note
can currently scan a maximum of 100 workspaces. Take this into account
when planning which workspaces you want to analyze.
:::

## Supported platforms

supports the following cloud platforms:

- [AWS](cv-aws-discovery.htm)

- [Azure](cv-onboard-azure.htm)

- [Google Cloud](cv-gcp-discovery.htm)
